---

<section id="why-us">
  <div class="wu-header reveal">
    <div class="stag">Why LUXEhome</div>
    <h2>The Standard You<br />Deserve, Delivered</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="wu-grid">

    <div class="wu-card reveal">
      <div class="wu-icon">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
          <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
          <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>500+ Projects Completed</h3>
      <p>
        Hundreds of floors, bathrooms, and staircases across Sri Lanka — each
        one finished to the same uncompromising standard.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wu-card reveal">
      <div class="wu-icon">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
          <path d="M21 12c-1 0-3-1-3-3V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4c0 2-2 3-3 3s3 1 3 3v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4c0-2 2-3 3-3z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Grade-A Materials Only</h3>
      <p>
        Tokyo cement and tile adhesive, Swisstek grout, and a professional tile
        leveling system on every job — no exceptions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wu-card reveal">
      <div class="wu-icon">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
          <path d="M7 9h2M11 9h6M7 13h10"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Transparent Pricing</h3>
      <p>
        Clear per sq.ft rates published upfront. No hidden charges, no
        surprises — just an honest quote before work begins.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wu-card reveal">
      <div class="wu-icon">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>One Team, Everything</h3>
      <p>
        From site visit and quote to tiling, plumbing, electrical, and ceiling —
        a single contractor you can rely on from start to finish.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background: var(--off-white);
    padding: 5.5rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Subtle diamond watermark */
  section::before {
    content: '◆';
    position: absolute;
    right: -2rem;
    bottom: -3rem;
    font-size: 22rem;
    color: rgba(196, 120, 74, .04);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    font-family: serif;
  }

  .wu-header {
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .wu-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .wu-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid var(--stone);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .85rem;
    transition: border-color .25s, transform .25s, box-shadow .25s;
  }

  .wu-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--clay);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(196, 120, 74, .1);
  }

  .wu-icon {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    background: rgba(196, 120, 74, .1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--clay);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background .25s;
  }

  .wu-card:hover .wu-icon {
    background: rgba(196, 120, 74, .18);
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  p {
    font-size: .86rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
  }

  /* Stagger card reveals */
  .wu-card:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0s; }
  .wu-card:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: .08s; }
  .wu-card:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: .16s; }
  .wu-card:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: .24s; }

  /* ── Responsive ── */

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    section { padding-left: 2.5rem; padding-right: 2.5rem; }
    .wu-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .wu-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
